reviews.review_text: Good times remembered Wow! Thanks for bringing me back 20 years. I'll never forget those 2 days in Eugene. We were working in Glacier National Park in Montana and got off and drove into Eugene for it. It just brings back memories and flashbacks thought long lost and forgotten. Ahh, to be young and on the loose again. It means so much to me to have this now. Thanks!

Great time had by all! The Music, Camping in the Parking lot, swimming in the river, the entire  body of fans made it an environment all its own.  

This old man would pick up all the empty beer cans in this really beat up truck, this went on  throughout the day and night he made trips out of the lot full!  I will never forget  seeing him drive away in a brand new truck while his son drove the beater on the last night.
